import React from 'react' const Rating = ({ value, text }) => { return (
= 1 ? "fa-solid fa-star" : value >= 0.5 ? "fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke" : "fa-sloid fa-star" } /> = 2 ? "fa-solid fa-star" : value >= 1.5 ? "fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke" : "fa-sloid fa-star" } /> = 3 ? "fa-solid fa-star" : value >= 2.5 ? "fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke" : "fa-sloid fa-star" } /> = 4 ? "fa-solid fa-star" : value >= 3.5 ? "fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke" : "" } /> = 5 ? "fa-solid fa-star" : value >= 4.5 ? "fa-regular fa-star-half-stroke" : "" } /> {text }
) } export default Rating
